Blevio - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia

Blevio ( Lombard: Biev or Blef (Western Lombard)) is a (municipality) in the Province of Como in the Italian region Lombardy, located about 40 kilometres (25 mi) north of Milan and about 2 kilometres (1 mi) northeast of Como. It overlooks the eastern shore of Lake Como from hilly slopes starting at more than 200 metres (660 ft).
